{"id": "1418891370801922089", "channel_id": "1418891370801922089", "type": 0, "author_id": "605159327942049844", "author_name": "ev_6185", "author_bot": false, "content": "今天我在翻譯卡斯托爾的通訊時發現了一個問題。雖然喚醒體體內，銀鑰內，通訊器內的，都叫「銀芯」可是GPT目前把它們有時翻譯成 “Silver Core” 有時翻譯成 “Silver Chip”。在重要名詞錄裡也查不到一個確切翻譯。所以請問到底該吧「銀芯科技」翻譯成 “Silver Chip Technology” 還是一如既往的 “Silver Core Technology”? \n\nI encountered a problem today while translating Castor’s texts. Despite what’s within awakeners, skey, and the communicator all being called “銀芯”, the GPT translates it as “Silver core” sometimes and “silver chip” in others. A definitive translation couldn’t be found in the key terms index either. So I must ask whether I should translate “銀芯” technology as “Silver Chip” or “Silver Core”technology?", "timestamp": "2025-09-20T09:27:44.526000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-09-20T19:21:24.471000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1418891370801922089", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "銀芯科技到底該翻譯成什麼？(What’s the appropriate translation for “Silver Chip Technology”?)", "forum_channel_id": "1404748432328888401", "thread_tags": ["1404748529724952576", "1412867203514236942"], "is_thread_starter": true}
