{"id": "1418895132274458736", "channel_id": "1418891370801922089", "type": 0, "author_id": "183782216353054720", "author_name": "omnichromia", "author_bot": false, "content": "I will note for whatever it's worth that I have an understanding of the lore of this game that is pretty damn solid despite (I'm pretty sure) resting ENTIRELY on the use of the term \"Silver Chip Technology\";\n\nThat being that Silver has a curious property of being able to be used in electrical components to fuel advanced technology with the power of higher wills\n\nbasically magical motherboards powered by the souls of the dissoluted\n\nAnd that is either a great boon to the term Silver Chip OR a horrible, TRAGIC misunderstanding that can not be easily remedied\n\nBecause if I'm wrong about that aspect of Morimens worldbuilding whoooooo boy is there a lot of work to do <:PAIMON_DEAD:708170044848472105> because I don't think it's been explicitly described that way in the story at least as far as I've gotten, that's only been heavily implied", "timestamp": "2025-09-20T09:42:41.331000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-09-20T09:43:20.050000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1418891370801922089", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "銀芯科技到底該翻譯成什麼？(What’s the appropriate translation for “Silver Chip Technology”?)", "forum_channel_id": "1404748432328888401", "thread_tags": ["1404748529724952576", "1412867203514236942"]}
