{"id": "1419017318591238144", "channel_id": "1418891370801922089", "type": 19, "author_id": "605159327942049844", "author_name": "ev_6185", "author_bot": false, "content": "I think we have another “cool name problem” on our hands 💀", "timestamp": "2025-09-20T17:48:12.819000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["183782216353054720"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1418895132274458736", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1418891370801922089", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "銀芯科技到底該翻譯成什麼？(What’s the appropriate translation for “Silver Chip Technology”?)", "forum_channel_id": "1404748432328888401", "thread_tags": ["1404748529724952576", "1412867203514236942"]}
{"id": "1419019502208942292", "channel_id": "1418891370801922089", "type": 0, "author_id": "605159327942049844", "author_name": "ev_6185", "author_bot": false, "content": "精純 should just be an abbreviation of 精湛純熟 . With 精湛 being the quality of being masterly (adept at something, masterfully executed, made, etc etc) and 純熟 being proficient. So really it’s just a cool name that implies the silver chip/core had been masterfully and proficiently made/extracted/distilled, etc. It reads to me as more of an indication of Silver core quality (because I’m 90% confident doll mentioned there are different quality tiers of silver cores) than it being the result of a manufacturing process - but that definition is also not off the table due to how *ambiguous* the word choice here is.", "timestamp": "2025-09-20T17:56:53.434000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1418891370801922089", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "銀芯科技到底該翻譯成什麼？(What’s the appropriate translation for “Silver Chip Technology”?)", "forum_channel_id": "1404748432328888401", "thread_tags": ["1404748529724952576", "1412867203514236942"]}
{"id": "1419020249189056512", "channel_id": "1418891370801922089", "type": 0, "author_id": "605159327942049844", "author_name": "ev_6185", "author_bot": false, "content": "If the intentions of the world builder are to use this name to indicate quality then “Exquisite Silver” would be my suggestion.", "timestamp": "2025-09-20T17:59:51.528000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1418891370801922089", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "銀芯科技到底該翻譯成什麼？(What’s the appropriate translation for “Silver Chip Technology”?)", "forum_channel_id": "1404748432328888401", "thread_tags": ["1404748529724952576", "1412867203514236942"]}
{"id": "1419020526214713475", "channel_id": "1418891370801922089", "type": 0, "author_id": "605159327942049844", "author_name": "ev_6185", "author_bot": false, "content": "I wouldn’t go as far as preeminent unless this is the highest tier - which as far as I’m aware of is used to make awakeners.", "timestamp": "2025-09-20T18:00:57.576000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1418891370801922089", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "銀芯科技到底該翻譯成什麼？(What’s the appropriate translation for “Silver Chip Technology”?)", "forum_channel_id": "1404748432328888401", "thread_tags": ["1404748529724952576", "1412867203514236942"]}
